

'''Greg Martin is a a young independent researcher into alternative currencies and their applicaton to online communities.'''


=Bio=

"My name is Greg Martin (1979) and I live in Newfoundland, Canada. I have a
general interest in P2P and open source concepts where they apply to
education, spirituality, politics, but especially economics. I am interested
in projects to develop alternative currencies and implement them through
online communities. My goal is to gather and share information about these
projects, to network with the people involved and help them network with
each other."


